<p>MAF (Layout)</p>

<p>There are Panel stretch layout and Deck as new components in this group. <br />
Also there is a fragment to keep an entire page inside of it and accepts attributes and methods.</p>

<ul>
  <li><img src="/images/2015-09-21-differences-maf-and-adf-mobile/amxLayoutMAF.JPG" alt="" /></li>
