<p>MAF (Operations)</p>

<p>There is a new component called Client listener that gives you a declarative way to register a Javascript listener that will be executed when a specific event type is fired.</p>

<ul>
  <li><img src="/images/2015-09-21-differences-maf-and-adf-mobile/amxOperationsMAF.JPG" alt="" /></li>
